    <div class="crowd-tip"><strong>Best time:</strong> Monday to Wednesday mornings during summer for the quietest palace interior experience. Weekends in June–August are the busiest. The park surrounding the palace is free and less crowded than the interior at all times. The palace is only open on weekends from January to April and October to December.</div>
